Add LinkedIn or LinkedIn Sales Navigator profiles to your Overloop campaigns in just 1 click!

- Scrape LinkedIn profiles, find their verified emails, and add them to your outreach campaigns directly with the Overloop Chrome Extension.
- Add and enrich new leads in bulk from LinkedIn search or the Sales Navigator lists.
- Avoid duplicates by excluding leads that are already in your Overloop account.
